OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe First and deputy First Ministers
OL,8,Fhave defended the Stormont Executive's
OL,9,Fperformance over the last year.
OL,11,FMichelle O'Neill and Emma Little-
OL,12,FPengelly spoke during a visit to a day
OL,13,Fnursery in east Belfast following the
OL,14,Fpublication of a report tracking
OL,15,Fprogress towards the Programme for
OL,16,FGovernment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe SDLP described the report as
OL,8,F"empty" and while the Executive argued
OL,9,Fit has been successful in helping
OL,10,Ffamilies with childcare costs and in
OL,11,Freducing waiting lists, ministers said
OL,12,Fthey know there is more to be done.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe programme, which runs to 2027,
OL,8,Fsets out nine priorities which include
OL,9,Freforming public services, growing a
OL,10,Fglobally competitive and sustainable
OL,11,Feconomy, more affordable childcare,
OL,12,Fcutting health waiting times, ending
OL,13,Fviolence against women and girls,
OL,14,Fbetter support for children and young
OL,15,Fpeople with special educational needs
OL,16,Fand protecting Lough Neagh.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FMore than 20,000 families have been
OL,8,Fhelped with the cost of childcare over
OL,9,Fthe last year. Ministers have pointed
OL,10,Fto that as a success as well as
OL,11,Ftransforming public services however
OL,12,Fthey recognise there is more work to
OL,13,Fdo.
OL,15,FThe First Minister said: "There's a
OL,16,Fsignificant difference being made to
OL,17,Fpeople's lives, albeit not even as
OL,18,Ffast as I would want to see it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"What I would encourage people to take
OL,8,Ffrom this`look at what we've achieved
OL,9,Fin this past year in terms of the
OL,10,FProgram for Government, but I'm more
OL,11,Ffixated on what are we going to
OL,12,Fachieve in the next year and the years
OL,13,Fto come.
OL,15,F"We will fulfill the commitments that
OL,16,Fwe've set out in the Programme for
OL,17,FGovernment," Michelle O'Neill added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"Ultimately, politics is about
OL,8,Fimproving people's lives. I want them
OL,9,Fto feel that from what we've done thus
OL,10,Ffar, but I would say it's a work in
OL,11,Fprogress. There's lots more to be
OL,12,Fdone. There's no room for complacency
OL,13,Fhere."
OL,15,FThe Deputy First Minister said:
OL,16,F"They're not the things you
OL,17,Fnecessarily see on the headlines, but
OL,18,Fthey are making a difference to
OL,19,Fpeople's lives.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"That's why we hope that the depth
OL,8,Fwithin this report, showing that it's
OL,9,Fnot just the headline-grabbers
OL,10,Fnecessarily, it's all of those
OL,11,Fdifferent elements that demonstrate an
OL,12,Fimprovement right across the system.
OL,14,F"As Michelle has said, we are not
OL,15,Fcomplacent. We recognise that people
OL,16,Fare still frustrated. We recognise
OL,17,Fthere still needs to be a huge amount
OL,18,Fdone," Emma Little-Pengelly added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"I think what this report will
OL,8,Findicate is a good start, but (there
OL,9,Fwill be) much more work that will
OL,10,Fhappen over the course of not just the
OL,11,Fnext 12 months, but indeed for the
OL,12,Fyears ahead as well."
OL,14,FThe Programme for Government progress
OL,15,Freport lists that over the last year
OL,16,Fthe Executive invested #135 million to
OL,17,Fcut waiting lists, worked to improve
OL,18,FSpecial Educational Needs provision
OL,19,Fand completed some actions to reverse
OL,20,Fthe pollution of Lough Neagh.
OL,26,@pD@_pmqD@Hpn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe report does not mention that the
OL,8,FExecutive has yet to deliver an anti-
OL,9,Fpoverty strategy and that no budget
OL,10,Fhas been agreed.
OL,12,FMinisters again insisted that the
OL,13,Fgovernment at Westminster needs to
OL,14,Fgive Stormont more money to enable
OL,15,Fthem to improve public services.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
