PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779977469
OL,3,CFirst and deputy First Ministers
OL,4,Cdefend Executive's performance over
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FLeader of the Opposition Matthew
OL,8,FO'Toole MLA said: "Today's photo ops
OL,9,Fare simply not good enough in the
OL,10,Fcontext of refusing to set a budget
OL,11,Fand spending every day of every week
OL,12,Fof every month`other than the odd
OL,13,Fphoto op`at one another's throats and
OL,14,Fengaging in engineered rows. The
OL,15,Fpublic see through it."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
